manpage:
&site;



    This page describes the directory layout in svn.




    The layout of WebTest in svn does not follow the usual directory layout, but follows this set-up:




                https://github.com/canoo/webtest

            is the the head of the development in GitHub;




                https://github.com/canoo/webtest/releases

            contains the last successive builds of WebTest in GitHub;




                https://svn.canoo.com/versions/webtest

            contains the earlier successive builds of WebTest in Subversion;




                https://svn.canoo.com/releases/webtest

            contains the successive releases of WebTest in Subversion.
